This folder is for figure images associated with the user reference documentation for DRAGONS primitives only.

All images should have a filename consistent with the general DRAGONs file name conventions,

e.g.

geminidr.core.primitives_ccd.CCD.biasCorrect_biasImageExample01.png

The image can then be included in the relevant documentation page by including a line in the relevant main
.rst file of the primitive, (e.g. primitive_biasCorrect.rst) as follows:

.. image:: ./images/geminidr.core.primitives_ccd.CCD.biasCorrect_biasImageExample01.png
